III.
General Comments on Platform Differences.

The .save files are from an x86_64 platform and with gfortran either:
gcc version 7.5.0 (Ubuntu 7.5.0-3ubuntu1~18.04)
or
Linux 3.10.0-1160.133.1.el7.x86_64 #1 SMP Thu Mar 6 03:04:40 EST 2025 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server release 7.9 (Maipo)
gcc version 7.3.0 (GCC) 

Other similar operating systems and compilers tend to show differences mainly
in floating point arithmetic.

32 bit platforms tend to show more differences, and the causes include
binary file formats and memory layouts as well as floating point arithmetic.
